---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-visual reveal">
        <div class="image-wrapper">
          <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/hero-about.webp" type="image/webp" />
          <img src="/images/hero-about.jpg" alt="Medea Clinic Interior" />
        </picture>
          <div class="overlay-frame"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-badge">
          <strong>No.1</strong>
          <span>Hollywood Smile<br>Specijalisti</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="section-label">O klinici</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Dobrodošli u<br><em>MEDEA CLINIC</em></h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="divider reveal"></div>
        
        <p class="section-body reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Moderna stomatološka klinika gdje se vrhunska stručnost susreće sa najnovijom tehnologijom i maksimalnim komforom za svakog pacijenta. Na raspolaganju su vam 4 savremeno opremljene ordinacije, dizajnirane po najvišim standardima.
        </p>

        <ul class="check-list reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <li>4 savremeno opremljene ordinacije po najvišim standardima</li>
          <li>Specijalizovani za kompleksne estetske i protetske zahvate</li>
          <li>Besplatne konsultacije za svaki zahvat</li>
          <li>Tamo gdje drugi staju — MEDEA CLINIC stvara Hollywood osmijeh</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="about-actions reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="tel:061828888" class="btn-primary">061 828 888</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about {
    padding: 10rem 0;
    background: var(--dark);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 5%;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-visual {
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.2);
  }

  .image-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 1s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .about-visual:hover .image-wrapper img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .overlay-frame {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.3);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2rem;
    right: -2rem;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--black);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 180px;
    box-shadow: 20px 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .about-badge strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-badge span {
    font-size: .75rem;
    letter-spacing: .1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.4;
    display: block;
  }

  .check-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .check-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .check-list li::before {
    content: '';
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: .6rem;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .about-actions {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .about-grid {
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    #about {
      padding: 6rem 0;
    }
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .about-visual {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 4rem;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .about-badge {
      right: 0;
      bottom: -1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      min-width: 150px;
    }
  }
</style>
